data.description: This 2-story farmhouse has 3 bedrooms, 1 bath and is located on a corner section of a 5.4-acre plot on two parcels. There are stables, a barn, pastures and your very own creek. The house has a metal roof, original flooring and wood siding. Large kitchen and living room area with a freestanding wood stove providing heat to the home. The water system is a gravity fed spring box reservoir. A very unique property. This home is being sold in "AS IS" condition.
